<p>Nicole wore her tumbling raven locks in a loose wavy style, and highlighted her striking features with a bronze pallet of make-up including a sparkling eye look.</p>

<p>She captioned the sizzling snaps: 'Drop your fav purple emoji. #TheMaskedSinger.'  </p>

<p>During the evening's episode of the show, contestant Mickey Rourke shocked the panel and audience alike by pulling off his gremlin mask prematurely. </p>

